<p>701. Also at the same meeting, at the request of the representative of Norway, a recorded 
vote was taken on draft resolution A/HRC/12/L.13/Rev.1. The draft resolution was adopted 
by 26 votes in favour, 15 against, with 6 abstentions. The voting was as follows: 
</p>
